</P>
<P>
TOP PHOTO: Tableware from the <ORGANIZATION>Elegant Table</ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION>Brentwood</LOCATION>, and <ORGANIZATION>Tesoro</ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION>Los 
Angeles</LOCATION>. 
</P>
<P>
BOTTOM PHOTO: Tableware from <ORGANIZATION>Geary's North</ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION>Beverly Hills</LOCATION>, and <ORGANIZATION>Tesoro</ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION>Los 
Angeles</LOCATION>. 
</P></TEXT>
