<LEADPARA>  Chefs from 25 restaurants and 21 wineries will participate in San Francisco's
Taste of the Nation benefit, from 6 to 10 p.m. on May 22 at Le Meridien Hotel.
It is one of 80 such events across the country sponsored by S.O.S./Bon Appetit
